SegPay,is,a,billing,platform,for,handling,credit,cards,checks,and,European,direct,debit,authorizations,The,platform,comes,with,marketing,tools,sales,reporting,automated,password,management,and,an,online,web,interface,It,can,provide,payment,portals,in,multiple,languages,and,accept,a,variety,of,currencies,Many,of,SegPay,s,functions,are,accessible,programmatically,via,SOAP,calls